      • startTask

        public void startTask​(User user,
                      int taskID)
        Start a new task. If a user is not already present in the team roster (and taskID is valid) a new StatisticsSet is created. If a StatisticsSet is already present (and taskID isn't already in use), set current task with task id, add 1 to the number of tasks attempted, and adjust completion percentage as well as taskblasterrating.
        Parameters:
        user - user
        taskID - ID of task
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - if user is null
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if taskID is 0 or negative
